[This answer][1] helped me to resolve my problem.


  [1]: https://stackoverflow.com/a/56893656/9753003

I created an abstract class:

    @DataJpaTest
    @AutoConfigureTestDatabase(replace = AutoConfigureTestDatabase.Replace.NONE)
    @DirtiesContext(classMode = DirtiesContext.ClassMode.BEFORE_CLASS)
    public abstract class BaseDataJpaTest {}

And inherit all my `@DataJpaTest` from this class.
This way I get a fresh context before each test.

